{"tid":2123883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港次季經濟恐縮9.5% 令香港經濟陷入史無前例的困境！","createTime":"2020-07-25T04:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T10:47:24.000Z","uid":137088,"like":175,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce119e5b5bc5f1ff6ef79ad1030af6809f683d0","tid":2123883,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E6%AC%A1%E5%AD%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%81%90%E7%B8%AE9-5-214500642.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%25B8%25AE9-5-214500642.html&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=b26c56c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E6%AC%A1%E5%AD%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%81%90%E7%B8%AE9-5-214500642.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情令香港經濟陷入史無前例的困境！英國研究機構牛津經濟研究院（Oxford Economics）預警，下周三公布的本港今年第二季本地生產總值（GDP）恐按年萎縮9.5%，換言之將再創一九七四年有紀錄以來的最大跌幅。分析認為，疫情不至於會觸發金融風險，衰退亦總會過去，但之後何去何從，政府應好好籌劃。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，今年首季GDP按年急插8.9%，已創有紀錄以來最差，若次季跌幅如上述預期，則顯示香港經濟危機更嚴峻。Oxford Economics資深經濟師Tommy Wu還估計，本港今年全年GDP恐萎縮6%，即為迄今最差、較正值亞洲金融風暴時的一九九八年縮5.9%還惡劣，要是目前這波疫情拖得更久，幾個月內恐出現更大規模的企業倒閉潮，指「不確定性很多，前景不容樂觀」。"},{"pid":"afd2fde6d8a8aa9b6b0efea9a68ebb79f1f75a91","tid":2123883,"uid":276440,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"政府先係攬炒元兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b54cac52467d17dd625057d877274e21f6db1f","tid":2123883,"uid":137088,"like":155,"dislike":4,"score":151,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"股市樓市繼續平衡時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e898fa62e1b1502d98f1df0b06516b8125204f5b","tid":2123883,"uid":289708,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"政府: 樓價唔跌沒事兒"},{"pid":"3dd544c76e15229